The American Civil Liberties Union (ACLU) released a report critical of the militarization of law enforcement in June of 2014.15 The report argued that LEAs, specifically their Special Weapons and Tactics (SWAT) teams, were deploying heavily armed officers using dangerous tactics in situations that did not call for such heavy-handed responses. The report indicated that the number of SWAT deployments had increased
